					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13198359#post-4660571</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13198359/scp-4658#post-4660571</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sun, 24 May 2020 08:27:37 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>LordBlackLotus</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>6449008</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>This is odd. I'm not sure why the controller exudes wax of all things but it's a pretty interesting concept.</p> <p>Only thing I have issue with is the psychological screening of the D-class. It was mentioned once but never explained why; the effects of the controller seemed to make game consoles mate and produce offspring but never anything else mentioned about humans or the possible idea of it either. That throws it off enough for me to give a no-vote.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
